==== Root File Instructions ====

0. Start TBrowser
new TBrowser

1. Total Hit Map:
Hits->Draw("fY:fX", "", "colz");

2. Energy per Layer:
Hits->Draw("DetectorID", "EnergyDep", "hist");

3. Side View:
Hits->Draw("fY:fZ", "", "colz");

4. Individual Hit Maps:

TCanvas *c1 = new TCanvas("c1", "Beam Spot per Layer", 1200, 800);

c1->Divide(5, 4);

for (int i = 0; i < 19; i++) {
    c1->cd(i + 1); 
    Hits->Draw("fY:fX", Form("DetectorID == %d", i), "colz");
}